  "A city planner examines a frequency table of daily traffic counts at an intersection: 0-99 cars (2 days), 100-199 (8 days), 200-299 (12 days), 300-399 (6 days), 400-499 (2 days). Over the 30-day period, what percentage of days had fewer than 300 cars?": "",
  "22 days or about 73%": "",
  "28 days or about 93%": "",
  "12 days or 40%": "",
  "20 days or about 67%": "",
